      <description>&lt;p&gt;Hello! I&amp;rsquo;m a &lt;strong&gt;full-stack&lt;/strong&gt; software developer. I&amp;rsquo;ve been building &lt;a href=&#34;https://hdwr.co&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;iOS apps&lt;/a&gt; with Swift since 2015, &lt;a href=&#34;https://gusto.com&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;web apps&lt;/a&gt; with Ruby on Rails since 2009, and &lt;strong&gt;QBASIC&lt;/strong&gt; games since 1995. I also enjoy working on &lt;strong&gt;devops&lt;/strong&gt;, and &lt;strong&gt;embedded software&lt;/strong&gt; for the &lt;strong&gt;Raspberry Pi&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Arduino&lt;/strong&gt;. I prefer &lt;strong&gt;working remotely&lt;/strong&gt; on distributed teams.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I have qualified for an &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.uscis.gov/working-united-states/temporary-workers/o-1-visa-individuals-extraordinary-ability-or-achievement&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;O-1 visa&lt;/a&gt;, and I have passed the &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.toptal.com/top-3-percent&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34;&gt;Toptal screening process&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I may be available to work on your project. Please &lt;a href=&#34;#contact&#34;&gt;contact me&lt;/a&gt; for availability and rates.&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
